OL,3,CFarmer fears pressure of the job
OL,4,Cpushing farmers to take their own life
OL,6,FA second-generation farmer from
OL,7,FSomerset has told ITV News long hours,
OL,8,Fisolation and financial struggles are
OL,9,Fall contributing to declining mental
OL,10,Fwellbeing in the industry.
OL,12,FRichard Payne, from Manor Farm,
OL,13,FHeathfield near Taunton, took over the
OL,14,Fbusiness from his father in 1985, but
OL,15,Fsaid the pressures on those working in
OL,16,Fthe sector are unsustainable.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV News, he said: "Food
OL,19,Fis the only thing we need every day of
OL,20,Fthe year, and yet it's perceived as
OL,21,Fvalueless.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
