OL,3,CFarmer fears pressure of the job
OL,4,Cpushing farmers to take their own life
OL,6,F"I know of two people locally here who
OL,7,Fhave very sadly taken their own lives.
OL,8,FIt's just awful. No one should be put
OL,9,Fin that position."
OL,11,FMr Payne added that the upcoming
OL,12,Fgovernment changes to subsidies and
OL,13,Ftaxes have left some farmers
OL,14,Fstruggling to cope with the added
OL,15,Fpressure.
OL,17,F"There are some people who feel that
OL,18,Fif they're ill or very old, before the
OL,19,Fend of this financial year, they're
OL,20,Fconsidering the ultimate sacrifice.
OL,21,FIt's totally wrong.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
