OL,3,CFarmer fears pressure of the job
OL,4,Cpushing farmers to take their own life
OL,6,F"If we want to protect farming and
OL,7,Fhave a fit, healthy workforce doing
OL,8,Fit, we have to do better, a lot
OL,9,Fbetter."
OL,11,FThe Farm Safety Foundation said the
OL,12,Fmental health of UK farmers is at a
OL,13,Ffour-year low, with figures showing
OL,14,Fthere were 47 suicides in the sector
OL,15,Fin 2024 ` a 7% increase from 2022.
OL,17,FThe research also found that 95% of
OL,18,Ffarmers under 40 believe mental health
OL,19,Fis the biggest hidden issue for those
OL,20,Fworking in agriculture.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
