OL,3,CFarmer fears pressure of the job
OL,4,Cpushing farmers to take their own life
OL,6,FStephanie Berkeley, Manager of the
OL,7,FFarm Safety Foundation, is calling on
OL,8,Ffarmers, rural organisations and
OL,9,Fcolleges to start life-saving
OL,10,Fconversations.
OL,12,F"We have made significant strides in
OL,13,Fraising awareness and improving
OL,14,Feducation around mental health, but
OL,15,Fwhen it comes to suicide prevention,
OL,16,Fprogress has been far more limited,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
