OL,3,CFarmer fears pressure of the job
OL,4,Cpushing farmers to take their own life
OL,6,F"Farming brings a unique set of
OL,7,Fpressures - long hours, isolation,
OL,8,Ffinancial uncertainty, generational
OL,9,Fexpectations and physical risk.
OL,11,F"Conversations about suicide in rural
OL,12,Fcommunities require approaches that
OL,13,Fare real, relatable and rooted in
OL,14,Flived experience.
OL,16,F"Without training designed for the
OL,17,Frealities of agricultural life, we
OL,18,Frisk leaving those most vulnerable
OL,19,Fwithout the tools they need to
OL,20,Frecognise warning signs and intervene
OL,21,Feffectively."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
