OL,3,CFarmer fears pressure of the job
OL,4,Cpushing farmers to take their own life
OL,6,FMr Payne added: "I think the main
OL,7,Fpressures on farmers are loneliness
OL,8,Fand isolation, lack of profitability
OL,9,Fand the lack of worth from the
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,F"You never leave the job, our homes
OL,13,Fand the farm are our office, so when
OL,14,Ftimes are hard, you cannot leave work
OL,15,Fat work. It is very pervasive.
OL,17,F"Looking at my son now, the situation
OL,18,Ffinancially in farming is worse now
OL,19,Fthan it was 30-40 years ago, so my son
OL,20,Fhas no hope. It's a non-starter for
OL,21,Fhim to follow in my footsteps."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
