OL,3,CFarmer fears pressure of the job
OL,4,Cpushing farmers to take their own life
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat MP for Glastonbury
OL,7,Fand Somerton, Sarah Dyke, who is from
OL,8,Fa farming family, said one of her
OL,9,Ffriends at agricultural college took
OL,10,Fhis own life because of the pressures
OL,11,Fof the job.
OL,13,FShe said: "I remember his parents
OL,14,Ftelling me that he had left a note
OL,15,Fsaying I hope that, with my death, the
OL,16,Finsurance money will cover being able
OL,17,Fto make the farm successful. That's
OL,18,Fhow stark it is.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
