OL,3,CFarmer fears pressure of the job
OL,4,Cpushing farmers to take their own life
OL,6,F"Looking at younger farmers as they
OL,7,Ftransition from college and university
OL,8,Fback into the farm, they find
OL,9,Fthemselves quite isolated, and it
OL,10,Fbecomes really difficult.
OL,12,F"The pressures of life are on their
OL,13,Fshoulders as they are seen to be the
OL,14,Fones taking the business forward or
OL,15,Fperhaps being the ones to close the
OL,16,Ffarm gates for the very last time."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
