OL,3,CFarmer fears pressure of the job
OL,4,Cpushing farmers to take their own life
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,8,F(Defra) said: "Farmers are at the
OL,9,Fheart of our food security and
OL,10,Fenvironmental stewardship.
OL,12,F"Their mental health and wellbeing
OL,13,Fmatters, and we want to ensure they
OL,14,Fcan access support when they need it.
OL,16,F"We know that farmers and rural
OL,17,Fcommunities face real pressures, and
OL,18,Fwe continue to listen to their
OL,19,Fconcerns so that we can better respond
OL,20,Fto the difficulties they face."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
